col9:
if the mushroom has the following properties (simultaneously)
  • mushroom does not have odour and
  • mushroom can be sniffed easilysp;
then the mushroom is edible
col16:
if the mushroom has the following properties (simultaneously)
  • mushroom does not have odour and
  • population is scattered 
then the mushroom is edible
col25: Rule 1 contains attributes obviously mutually exclusive: conditions no odour and easy to sniff are contradictory.
